 "display": {
  "title": {
   "translate": "The Cataclysm Codex"
  },
  "subtitle": {
   "text": "Ancient Remnant. Maledictus. Ignis. The Leviathan. Each one is a door. The Codex is the key."
  },
  "description": [
   "◆━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━◆",
   "  CH.09 · THE CATACLYSM CODEX",
   "◆━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━◆",
   "",
   "▸ The Cataclysm mod adds a boss chain",
   "  that begins before the End and ends",
   "  deep inside it.",
   "  The Codex scroll maps the whole chain.",
   "  Get it early. The chain is long.",
   "",
   "◈ CATACLYSM BOSS SEQUENCE",
   "  └ ✦ Ancient Remnant: first gate",
   "    Found in dimensional ruin structures",
   "    Drops: Remnant Eye, Cataclysm armor fragments",
   "    Required to progress to Maledictus",
   "  └ ✦ Maledictus: the cursed form",
   "    Intermediate boss, drops Cursium",
   "    Cursium = crafting gate for Ignis/Annihilator tier",
   "  └ ✦ Ignited Revenant: follows Maledictus",
   "    Fire-phase variant, drops Revenant materials",
   "  └ ✦ Ignis: full fire boss, post-Cursium",
   "    Major loot gate, drops Ignitium",
   "    Ignitium = high-tier Cataclysm crafting material",
   "  └ ✦ Netherite Monstrosity: Nether depth boss",
   "    Drops Lacrima (triggers Infernal Age in Ch12)",
   "  └ ✦ The Leviathan: ocean/deep variant",
   "    Ch09-10 accessible, drops end-tier loot",
   "  └ ✦ Ender Guardian + Harbinger + Primordial",
   "    Post-portal (Ch13) — require End access",
   "",
   "◈ SCROLL: The Cataclysm Codex",
   "  └ 20% drop from: Ignis, Ancient Remnant,",
   "    The Leviathan",
   "  └ Research time: 30 min",
   "  └ Unlocks: full Cataclysm boss chain knowledge,",
   "    crafting pathway for Ignitium tier",
   "",
   "◈ CURSIUM ALERT",
   "  └ Maledictus → Cursium",
   "  └ Cursium is the crafting gate for the",
   "    strongest Cataclysm gear (Ch11+)",
   "  └ Farm Maledictus before Ch11 progression",
   "",
   "▸ The Ancient Remnant was not created by the Ender.",
   "  It predates the End itself.",
   "  The Cataclysm began somewhere else.",
   "  The scroll does not say where.",
   "",
   "▶ Find The Cataclysm Codex scroll [check]",
   "▶ Defeat the Ancient Remnant [check]",
   "",
   "◇ Netherite Monstrosity drops Lacrima.",
   "  Lacrima triggers the Infernal Age (Ch12).",
   "  Do not farm it until you are ready for Ch12."
  ],
